1.6
log
@Replace the MVME376 driver from a homemade and dusty if_ve driver to
a ``regular'' if_le driver, sharing the common am7990 code.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: if_vereg.h,v 1.5 2003/10/11 22:08:57 miod Exp $ */

/*-
